    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "so if the escrow company is just a neutral third party, what exactly is their main job during those weeks? i'm just worried about the money just sitting there and what happens if the seller tries to pull something or if the inspection goes bad. does the escrow agent actually do anything besides just holding the cash?",
